{"tid":669054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】在麥當勞叔叔旁邊大方露內褲的妹　竟是全裸女僕","createTime":"2018-05-18T07:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T11:51:10.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab3b455dd3fa885bf34f12dbcbd2c0b95e3d2bb","tid":669054,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"據泰國《truststoreonline》網站報導，近日泰國的社交網路上瘋傳一組圖片，一名女子公開在一間麥當勞內，當眾掀裙露出小內褲，還微微張腿做出不雅動作。但事後有網友發現，這名女子就是先前以全裸女僕走紅的的明葛慕特。明葛慕特在今年2月與另外一名女模受到一間新開幕的咖啡店「COFFEE ON DAY」邀請，在店內進行全裸女僕的宣傳，更大打「大奶微微」廣告，兩人露出傲人胸圍吸客，還說：「這裡的咖啡很好喝，會加很多奶喔！」但消息一傳出，立刻被警方盯上，當時業者蘇空(Prasong Sukkorn)也被警方約談。<br />\n而如今明葛慕特的露內褲照再度引發討論，並引來泰國麥當勞公司的注意，揚言不排除提告。泰國麥當勞更指出，經調查後發現，這組露內褲的照片是在去年拍攝的，直至最近才被曝光與瘋傳。而明葛慕特本人目前沒有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180518/1356165/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180518%2F1356165%2F&d=4aislN5SURMOPut2E0JZv%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6f4a9db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180518%2F1356165%2F&h=af13bf7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180518/1356165/</a><br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180518/640_0320a24a2ee9e128bf04dbc55a81658d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180518%2F640_0320a24a2ee9e128bf04dbc55a81658d.jpg&h=34e4d41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180518/640_302c77162abeb95b4186c47010b4eda5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180518%2F640_302c77162abeb95b4186c47010b4eda5.jpg&h=6d137285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180518/640_964c4cb4482ecb83bbb0c5f25d9d08d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180518%2F640_964c4cb4482ecb83bbb0c5f25d9d08d7.jpg&h=981cad63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180518/640_713d1659ffe9bc1d1c8c32d176551854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180518%2F640_713d1659ffe9bc1d1c8c32d176551854.jpg&h=4280f450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84449412861f0e42b9714278a1db64e73ec4776","tid":669054,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"067c9181720e9854ae27478cd4abbb3087d0195b","tid":669054,"uid":105738,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"有碼你想我睇what?"},{"pid":"589cfaa0483391f797479ecce84717253c35b6c6","tid":669054,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"瘋傳"},{"pid":"61e8081fd5685eac47dbcdf2c5f98edd258aede6","tid":669054,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"589cfaa0483391f797479ecce84717253c35b6c6","tid":669054,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"瘋傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"又"},{"pid":"7bc30e6be12d931a5828658da5604eadc7a5a5b5","tid":669054,"uid":100236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"近日<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泰國</span></span></ins></strong>的社交網路上瘋傳一組圖片，一名女子公開在一間麥當勞內"},{"pid":"246dc9cf9a2b2f0843660e04ee67978ef181b42b","tid":669054,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"假架D奶"},{"pid":"4b4b02ebb95ffd71c8cd41af36bb8a43697acdae","tid":669054,"uid":11